## How to Use

1. Browse the auto-generated entries below
2. Pick a week that resonates (architectural decision, business pivot,
   significant bug with a learning)
3. Run `/blog research week-NN` to get a research scaffolding for it
4. Write from `BLOG_POST_TEMPLATE.md` (read `VOICE_REFERENCE.md` first)

**Each week has two sections**:
- Auto-generated content (above the marker)
- Your manual notes (below the marker — preserved on re-run)

